#index 99c8a1d8f..0bce7937f 100644
#--- a/CHANGES.current
#+++ b/CHANGES.current
#@@ -7,6 +7,17 @@ the issue number to the end of the URL: https://github.com/swig/swig/issues/
# Version 4.4.0 (in progress)
# ===========================
# 
#+2025-05-10: jschueller, wsfulton
